headline: NextEra Energy Stock: This Long Call Spread Trade Might Earn $607
summary: Looking for charts that hold into the end of August and the beginning of September, the choice is NextEra Energy stock.  The short call in NextEra Energy stock will finance the long call.  The trade costs $3.93, or $393 per set of option contracts in NextEra Energy stock.
